name: America - Mountains, Plains and the Sea
description: This image, "America - Mountains, Plains and the Sea" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in this process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewer. The concept behind this image was to reflect the natural beauty in America (USA) from the mountains, over the plains and to the sea.
